  "text": "Initially, genotyping of the hBDNF locus was performed using PCR on DNA extracted from tail tips as described. [CITATION_1] To overcome technical difficulties sometimes encountered with this protocol, we developed a new primer set BDNF-F: 5′-TCCACCAGGTGAGAAGAGTGA-3′, and BDNF-R: 5′-GAGGCTCC AAAGGCACTTGA-3′, followed by restriction-enzyme analysis with BsaA1, which cleaves the Val allele.",
